{"word":"盎","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"盎"},{"type":"span","content":"àngㄤˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 古代的一种盆，腹大口小。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 盛（"},{"type":"span","content":"shèng","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":"），充盈：春意"},{"type":"span","content":"盎","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"然。诗意"},{"type":"span","content":"盎","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"然。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"cup; pot; bowl; abundant"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"盎"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àng","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从皿,央声。本义:腹大口小的盛物洗物的瓦盆)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"盎,盆也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"盎谓之缶。——《尔雅》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"盎中无斗米储。——《乐府诗集·东门行》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:盎盂相敲(比喻家庭口角)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 盎齐(浊酒)的省称"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"三曰盎齐。——《周礼·酒正》"}]]},{"title":"词性变化","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"盎"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àng","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  充溢"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"其生色也睟然,见于面,盎于背。——《孟子·尽心上》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  又如:兴趣盎然;盎盎(洋溢的样子,充盈的样子);盎溢(充盈洋溢)"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"盎然"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àngrán","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"形容气氛、趣味等浓厚的样子"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"今日洞庭,诗意盎然。——《珍珠赋》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"一路行来,有雨趣而无淋漓之苦,自然也就格外感到意兴盎然。——李健吾《雨中登泰山》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"春意盎然"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"盎司，盎斯"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àngsī,àngsī","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)[ounce(缩写oz)]"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)常衡制的一种质量单位,等于1/16磅,或约等于28.3495克"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(3)药衡制或金衡制的一种质量单位,等于480格令或31.1034768克"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【午集中】【皿字部】盎 ·康熙筆画：10　·部外筆画：5 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【唐韻】【集韻】烏浪切【韻會】【正韻】於浪切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"鴦去聲。【說文】盆也。【爾雅·釋器】盎謂之缶。【疏】瓦器也。可以節樂，可以盛水，盛酒。【揚子·方言】罃甈謂之盎。【後漢·逢萌傳】首戴瓦盎。【古樂府·東門行】盎中無斗儲。【譚子化書】湯盎投井，所以化雹也。　又盛貌。【孟子】盎於背。【註】其背盎盎然盛。【樓异嵩山賦】方春陽之盎盎。　又盎齊，酒名。【周禮·天官】酒正，辨五齊之名，三曰盎齊。【註】盎，猶翁也。盛而翁翁然蔥白也。　又門名。【三輔黃圖】長安城南，出東頭，第一門曰覆盎門。　又姓。見【姓苑】。　又【廣韻】烏朗切【集韻】【韻會】倚朗切【正韻】於黨切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"鴦上聲。義同。　【說文】或作"},{"type":"span","content":"㼜"},{"type":"text","content":"。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷五】【皿部】"},{"type":"span","content":"盎","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"盆也。从皿央聲。"},{"type":"span","content":"㼜"},{"type":"text","content":"，盎或从瓦。烏浪切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字","pinyin":["àng"],"radical":"皿","stroke":"五画","total_stroke":"十画","stroke_order":"丨フ一ノ丶丨フ丨丨一","input_method":{"bopomofo":"LKBT","number":"50102","unicode":"U+76CE","wubi":"MDLF"}}